{"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/ViewEnvironmentPropagating\/environment","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/viewenvironmentui\/viewenvironmentpropagating\/environment"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI","doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/ViewEnvironmentPropagating"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"environment","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ViewEnvironment","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you’d like to provide overrides for the environment as it flows through a node, you should conform to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving"},{"text":" and provide those overrides in ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customize(environment:)"},{"text":". E.g.:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["func customize(environment: inout ViewEnvironment) {","    environment.traits.mode = .dark","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, this property gets the environment by recursively walking to the root of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"propagation path, and applying customizations on the way back down. The invalidation path may be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interrupted if a node has set it’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"environmentAncestor"},{"type":"text","text":" to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", even if there is a node"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which specifies this node as an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"environmentDescendant"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’d like to update the return value of this variable and have those changes propagated through the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"propagation hierarchy, conform to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving"},{"type":"text","text":" and call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setNeedsEnvironmentUpdate()"},{"type":"text","text":" and wait"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for the system to call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"apply(context:)"},{"type":"text","text":" when appropriate (e.g. on the next layout pass for"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"text":"\/","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"text":" subclasses).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"important","name":"Important","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"type":"text","text":" conformers "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"must"}]},{"type":"text","text":" call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"applyEnvironmentIfNeeded()"},{"type":"text","text":" in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"viewWillLayoutSubviews()"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"layoutSubviews()"},{"type":"text","text":" respectively."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironment"},{"text":" that is flowing through the propagation hierarchy.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"ma